          <p>Fibre to the Premises — the highest quality connection type. Fibre runs directly to your building, enabling the fastest available speeds including Gigabit options.</p>
          <div class="rbp-nbn-tech-availability">
            <span class="rbp-nbn-avail-dot" style="background:#22c55e"></span>
            <span style="color:#059669;font-size:12px;font-weight:700">Best performance</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="rbp-nbn-tech-card" style="--nbn-accent:#06b6d4;--nbn-icon-bg:#cffafe;--nbn-icon-color:#0891b2">
          <div class="rbp-nbn-tech-icon">🔌</div>
          <h3>HFC</h3>
          <p>Hybrid Fibre Coaxial — fibre to the node, then existing cable to the premises. Supports strong speeds suitable for most business applications.</p>
          <div class="rbp-nbn-tech-availability">
            <span class="rbp-nbn-avail-dot" style="background:#3b82f6"></span>
