          <div class="rbp-nbn-tech-icon">📡</div>
          <h3>FTTN / FTTC</h3>
          <p>Fibre to the Node / Fibre to the Curb — fibre runs close to your premises with copper for the final connection. Speed varies by distance from node.</p>
